的完整 Gherkin 用例详见 `tests/bdd/matching.feature`。\n   130\t\n   131\t```ghe
rkin\n   132\tFeature: Mutual Like Creates Match\n   133\t  Scenario: Mutual lik
e triggers match and conversation\n   134\t    Given Alice liked Bob\n   135\t  
 And Bob has not yet liked Alice\n   136\t    When Bob likes Alice\n   137\t    
Then a match record should be created with status "matched"\n   138\t    And a c
onversation should be auto-created for Alice and Bob\n   139\t    And both users
should receive a match notification via Socket.io\n   140\t    And both users sh
ould see the new match in their match list\n   141\t\n   142\t  Scenario: One-wa
y like remains pending\n   143\t    Given Alice liked Bob\n   144\t    And Bob h
as not liked Alice\n   145\t    When the system checks for mutual like\n   146\t
   Then no match record should exist\n   147\t    And no conversation should be 
